Metadata

Description

Dataset name: Baseline data from Let’s Move It intervention trial

Baseline data from Let’s Move It intervention trial, described in detail at https://heinonmatti.github.io/baseline-visu/index.html

Metadata for search engines

  • Temporal Coverage: January 2015 - April 2016
  • Spatial Coverage: Southern Finland
  • Citation: Heino, M. T. J., Fried, E. I., Sund, R., Haukkala, A., Knittle, K. P., Borodulin, K., Uutela, A., Araujo-Soares, V., Vasankari, T., & Hankonen, N. (2019). Visualisation and network analysis of physical activity and its determinants: Demonstrating opportunities in analysing baseline associations in the Let’s Move It trial.
  • URL: https://doi.org/10.31234/osf.io/46rzm
  • Identifier: 10.31234/osf.io/46rzm

  • Date published: Not yet published

  • Creator:Matti TJ Heino

    • measurementTechnique: Online survey, bioimpedance, accelerometer
